..TEXT:
|squilla~: The bell of Compline (Italian ^compieta~,
Latin ^dies completa~).  Cf. Dante's ^canzone~ "Cos@i nel mio
parlar," ^Rime~ CIII, 69: "Con esse passerei vespero e squille."
("I would pass with them Vesper and evening bells.")
