..TEXT:
|ch$e 'l velo @e ora ben tanto sottile~: It is the
^event~, the literal happening here, that is to be viewed as
disclosing now, in the mode of scriptural allegory, a "true"
meaning.  See ^Inf.~ IX, 61-63.
